<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="70" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="8.[151,1437,1762,2009]" pageId="8" pageNumber="70">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="70">
Valvae lineares-lanceolatae ad 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Pfitzer" authorityYear="1871" baseAuthorityName="Ehrenb." baseAuthorityYear="1843" box="[505,638,1762,1785]" class="Bacillariophyceae" family="Amphipleuraceae" genus="Frustulia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Chromista" order="Naviculales" pageId="8" pageNumber="70" phylum="Bacillariophyta" rank="species" species="rhomboides">rhomboides</taxonomicName>
, constriction dilute prope rotundatis polos. Longitudo 68.0–111.0 µm. Latitudo 17.5–21.0 µm. Striae 26–28/ 
<quantity box="[571,639,1798,1821]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="70" unit="mm" value="10.0">10 µm</quantity>
ad centro, 28/ 
<quantity box="[800,867,1798,1821]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="8" pageNumber="70" unit="mm" value="10.0">10 µm</quantity>
ad apices. Striae parallelae pro parte maxima, sed dilute convergentes et interdum undulatae ad apices, areolis lanceolatis ad apices et aream centralem, rotudatis alibi. Areolae extensae circa apices. Striae longitudinales parallelae trans valvam pro parte maxima, sed dilute undulatae ad valvam centrum. Interne areolae rotundatis et occlusis. Externe area centralis areolis parvis irregulariter aggregatis variabilibus numeri. Areolae serials in ambo latere raphis terminates ante extremis distalibus raphis.
</emphasis>
</paragraph>
